These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
City: nizza, new-york, hannover, rome
1. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
6. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person traveling to new-york##7
8. the chinese and the person traveling to rome have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person traveling to nizza have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | hannover   | rome     | new-york | nizza  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, bridge, whist
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the person playing canasta have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
6. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
8. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | whist     | bridge    | chess | canasta    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, white, blue
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes white##1
6. the person who likes white is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person who likes ivory and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | ivory    | white   | apricot    | blue  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

