.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, dancing, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | drawing | dancing | gardening  | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

