.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
House: ranch-style, cottage, modern, farmhouse
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the modern house is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the ranch-style house have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the cottage house have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
6. the cottage house is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the farmhouse house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | ranch-style | modern | farmhouse  | cottage |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

