.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, scientific, superhero
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, lawyer, police-officer, coach
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
4. the chef and the person watching scientific movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching superhero movies and the chef have different parity positions##9
6. the police-officer is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
7. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation | scientific | superhero |
| Nationality   | coach        | police-officer    | chef   | lawyer |

