1. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
2. the american is between the japanese and the dutch##2
3. the american and the fan salsa have different parity positions##9
4. the dutch is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the fan salsa is not to the right of the fan punk##8
6. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
7. the fan salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5

