.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, june, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
3. the person who's birthday is in august and the person driving the helicopter have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | january  | august  | june | december    |
| Transport     | taxi | trike | bike  | helicopter |

