.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, nectarine, peach
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, 7up, sprite
1. the person eating peach is not the person drinking sprite##6
2. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
3. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
6. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating garlic is the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the person eating peach and the person drinking water have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lemon   | peach    | nectarine | garlic    |
| Nationality   | sprite | water | 7up   | iced-tea |

