.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, amber, red, lilac
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, hedgehog, rat
1. the person who likes lilac and the owner of the cat have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who likes red is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
4. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person who likes amber##8
5. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hedgehog and the person who likes chestnut have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the cat and the person who likes red have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | chestnut | lilac | amber | red |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | fish   | rat        | cat            |

