3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the chaman-smoker and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | bolivar    | chaman | tiparillo | baccarat |
| Hobby      | puzzles | skydiving   | board-games   | baking   |

