.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, juice, water
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, radish, corn, pepper
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 3. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person eating corn##8
 4. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating nectarine is not the person drinking cola##6
 6. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking water and the person eating radish have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 9. the person drinking water is the person eating radish##1
10. the person drinking cola and the person eating radish have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice        | water   | coffee      |
| Hobby      | pepper | corn | radish | nectarine |

 